<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 08:10:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>该营唯一的女性是拯救受伤士兵生命的医生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/battalions-only-woman-is-doctor-who-saves-wounded-troops-lives/0000018c-69f2-d798-adac-edff42660000</link><description>27 岁的丹妮拉·阿加耶夫 (Daniella Agaev) 博士对她所在的营至关重要，她并不关心自己是团队中唯一的女性。自十月地面行动开始以来，她几乎没有离开过加沙，并拯救了许多战友的生命</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/battalions-only-woman-is-doctor-who-saves-wounded-troops-lives/0000018c-69f2-d798-adac-edff42660000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡顽固拒绝讨论“后天”也危及以色列军队在加沙的成就</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refusal-to-discuss-the-day-after-endangers-the-idfs-achievements-in-gaza/0000018c-69d3-de43-affd-fdd31add0000</link><description>在过去的几天里，该集团行动的沉重代价已经显而易见，而且可能会造成更多受害者。 ■ 以色列很快将不得不解决埃及的担忧，并且还将发现美国提供的支持是有条件的</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refusal-to-discuss-the-day-after-endangers-the-idfs-achievements-in-gaza/0000018c-69d3-de43-affd-fdd31add0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；以色列国防军打捞被杀哈马斯人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-live/senior-u-s-official-hamas-leader-sinwars-days-are-numbered/0000018c-6b87-db38-a9fc-eba7b5250000</link><description>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 美国高级官员：辛瓦尔的日子屈指可数，他手上沾满了美国人的鲜血 ■ 拜登希望以色列集中精力拯救加沙平民 ■ 摩萨德称七人因策划针对犹太人的恐怖袭击而在欧洲被捕代表哈马斯行动 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部称加沙有 18,608 人死亡、50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 03:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-live/senior-u-s-official-hamas-leader-sinwars-days-are-numbered/0000018c-6b87-db38-a9fc-eba7b5250000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼部长签署以色列国防军允许约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人在以色列定居点工作的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-okayed-decision-to-allow-west-bank-palestinians-to-work-in-settlements/0000018c-6a3b-db38-a9fc-ebbb9ccb0000</link><description>以色列国防军允许 10,000 名巴勒斯坦人在这些领土上的定居点和工厂工作，但他们仍被禁止进入以色列。一位国防消息人士称，“这纯粹是虚伪的：定居者酋长和部长反对他们进入以色列，但却是第一个要求他们在定居点工作的人”</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 01:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-okayed-decision-to-allow-west-bank-palestinians-to-work-in-settlements/0000018c-6a3b-db38-a9fc-ebbb9ccb0000</guid></item><item><title>“当人们热爱以色列并想住在这里时，即使他们不是犹太人，你能做什么？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-15/ty-article/.highlight/what-can-you-do-when-people-love-israel-and-want-to-live-here-even-if-theyre-not-jews/0000018c-6a9f-d798-adac-eebf41b40000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对以色列-摩尔多瓦夫妇因官僚主义而四分五裂，一位以色列食品专家通过采集和发酵工作坊帮助失去亲人的家庭应对悲伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 23:41:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-15/ty-article/.highlight/what-can-you-do-when-people-love-israel-and-want-to-live-here-even-if-theyre-not-jews/0000018c-6a9f-d798-adac-eebf41b40000</guid></item><item><title>“辛瓦尔告诉我：有一天我会掌权，而你将成为接受审讯的人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/sinwar-told-me-one-day-ill-be-in-power-and-youll-be-the-one-interrogated/0000018c-6a50-db38-a9fc-ebf2e85f0000</link><description>20 世纪 80 年代，负责审问叶海亚·辛瓦尔 (Yahya Sinwar) 的辛贝特审讯员讲述了他与哈马斯领导人的惊心动魄的遭遇。官员预测辛瓦尔将支持巴勒斯坦囚犯人质交换——但不会被以色列俘虏</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 23:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/sinwar-told-me-one-day-ill-be-in-power-and-youll-be-the-one-interrogated/0000018c-6a50-db38-a9fc-ebf2e85f0000</guid></item><item><title>塞法迪首席拉比谴责以色列士兵不尊重清真寺的照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/sephardic-chief-rabbi-decries-images-of-israeli-soldiers-disrespecting-mosques/0000018c-69bf-db38-a9fc-e9bf58740000</link><description>拉比伊扎克·约瑟夫（Yitzhak Yosef）写信给以色列国防军首席拉比，称士兵亵渎圣地的图像“对以色列人民及其在世界上的形象造成损害”，并表示应该向士兵解释“成员的感受”其他宗教的信仰不应受到伤害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 21:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/sephardic-chief-rabbi-decries-images-of-israeli-soldiers-disrespecting-mosques/0000018c-69bf-db38-a9fc-e9bf58740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列退伍军人在特别选举中被任命为共和党候选人，取代乔治·桑托斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-military-veteran-tapped-as-gop-candidate-in-special-election-to-replace-george-santos/0000018c-69f8-db38-a9fc-e9fafd2c0000</link><description>拿骚县议员、前以色列伞兵马兹·皮利普(Mazi Pilip)将在桑托斯空出的席位的特别选举中与民主党前国会议员汤姆·索兹(Tom Suozzi)对决</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 20:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-military-veteran-tapped-as-gop-candidate-in-special-election-to-replace-george-santos/0000018c-69f8-db38-a9fc-e9fafd2c0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅仅是否认暴行和悲凉：为什么这次巴勒斯坦民意调查很重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-14/ty-article/.highlight/not-only-atrocity-denial-and-desolation-why-this-palestinian-poll-matters/0000018c-696a-d798-adac-edef198b0000</link><description>在 10 月 7 日之前，巴勒斯坦政策和调查研究中心的这些发现将被认为对两国解决方案不利。现在他们应该给予安慰</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 19:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-14/ty-article/.highlight/not-only-atrocity-denial-and-desolation-why-this-palestinian-poll-matters/0000018c-696a-d798-adac-edef198b0000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲各地因恐怖阴谋联合调查逮捕七人，嫌疑人与哈马斯有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-14/ty-article/seven-individuals-arrested-across-europe-over-terror-plot-suspects-linked-to-hamas/0000018c-6948-d798-adac-edefd7dd0000</link><description>摩萨德周四在一份声明中表示，丹麦因“代表”哈马斯针对平民的恐怖阴谋而逮捕了七人。目前尚不清楚这七次逮捕是否指的是在欧洲进行的所有逮捕，或者是否还有丹麦当局未报告的其他逮捕事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 19:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-14/ty-article/seven-individuals-arrested-across-europe-over-terror-plot-suspects-linked-to-hamas/0000018c-6948-d798-adac-edefd7dd0000</guid></item><item><title>随着中国站在巴勒斯坦一边，加沙战争可能会加强以色列与台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-china-sides-with-palestinians-gaza-war-could-strengthen-israeli-ties-with-taiwan/0000018c-6842-dbd5-a39c-ff7356050000</link><description>中国媒体告诉世界，美国因欧洲和加沙战争而分心，可能会在一月份选举前危及台湾。然而，中国回应的一个副作用可能是促使以色列和台湾走得更近</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-china-sides-with-palestinians-gaza-war-could-strengthen-israeli-ties-with-taiwan/0000018c-6842-dbd5-a39c-ff7356050000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩南部的以色列缓冲区？贝鲁特政客忙于政党政治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-buffer-zone-in-south-lebanon-beirut-politicians-are-busy-with-party-politics/0000018c-686d-de5e-a3ef-6beddf560000</link><description>即使找到了将真主党赶出边境的纲领，黎巴嫩政界人士可能更关注谁填补该国空缺的总统职位，因为他们的政治和经济状况使得他们不太可能采取行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-buffer-zone-in-south-lebanon-beirut-politicians-are-busy-with-party-politics/0000018c-686d-de5e-a3ef-6beddf560000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的加沙堡垒是世界上独一无二的战场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-gaza-fortress-is-a-battlefield-like-no-other-in-the-world/0000018c-695a-db38-a9fc-e9fabcff0000</link><description>任何人如果问为什么拥有如此先进能力的以色列军队需要在加沙发动地面行动才能击败哈马斯，那么他并不了解该领土的独特挑战。以色列的所有选择都是致命的</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-gaza-fortress-is-a-battlefield-like-no-other-in-the-world/0000018c-695a-db38-a9fc-e9fabcff0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争紧张局势扰乱校园；布朗抗议者被捕；哈弗福德大楼被占用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/gaza-war-tensions-roil-campuses-brown-protesters-arrested-haverford-building-occupied/0000018c-68ec-d798-adac-ecef866e0000</link><description>数十名学生因抗议以色列在加沙的行动而拒绝离开大学大楼而被捕，这是一个月内的第二轮逮捕</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 17:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/gaza-war-tensions-roil-campuses-brown-protesters-arrested-haverford-building-occupied/0000018c-68ec-d798-adac-ecef866e0000</guid></item><item><title>禁止暴力定居者：美国和欧洲制定拒绝入境者的标准</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/banning-violent-settlers-u-s-europe-formulating-criteria-on-who-will-be-refused-entry/0000018c-6914-db38-a9fc-e9b632200000</link><description>随着针对暴力以色列定居者的国际行动势头增强，美国、英国和欧盟正在寻找方法，对那些在西岸对巴勒斯坦人实施暴力的人实施和执行签证禁令和其他限制</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 16:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/banning-violent-settlers-u-s-europe-formulating-criteria-on-who-will-be-refused-entry/0000018c-6914-db38-a9fc-e9b632200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡称10月7日的死亡人数与奥斯陆的死亡人数相同——更多的操纵和逃避责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-oct-7-death-toll-equal-to-oslos-a-comparison-that-does-not-bode-well/0000018c-6819-dbd5-a39c-ff7b56f20000</link><description>总理没有详细说明他的说法背后的计算，但进一步的检查表明这些数据可以被操纵，并且需要背景。最重要的是，内塔尼亚胡在这里也至少承担部分责任</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 14:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-oct-7-death-toll-equal-to-oslos-a-comparison-that-does-not-bode-well/0000018c-6819-dbd5-a39c-ff7b56f20000</guid></item><item><title>备受争议的汉娜·阿伦特奖颁奖典礼被推迟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/controversial-award-ceremony-for-the-hannah-arendt-prize-postponed/0000018c-6893-d798-adac-ecbf6f560000</link><description>玛莎·格森因在美国杂志《纽约客》的一篇文章中发表言论而受到批评，据说他们在文中将加沙的局势与二战期间被占领的欧洲犹太人聚居区进行了比较</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/controversial-award-ceremony-for-the-hannah-arendt-prize-postponed/0000018c-6893-d798-adac-ecbf6f560000</guid></item><item><title>拜登以色列和乌克兰政策背后的价值观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/the-values-behind-bidens-israel-and-ukraine-policies/0000018c-67f3-dbd5-a39c-fff3c7ee0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登对乌克兰和加沙战争及危机的处理堪称典范，迄今为止也是成功的。两国都很幸运，这些战争发生在一位既是自由干涉主义者又是现实主义者的领导人的领导下</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/the-values-behind-bidens-israel-and-ukraine-policies/0000018c-67f3-dbd5-a39c-fff3c7ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军与杰宁武装分子交火，三名巴勒斯坦人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-between-idf-and-gunmen-in-jenin/0000018c-6857-de5e-a3ef-6bff5f9a0000</link><description>以色列士兵被拍摄到在难民营中使用清真寺扬声器向难民营居民发出呼吁，并唱光明节歌曲。以色列国防军表示，这些士兵立即被解除执行任务</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-between-idf-and-gunmen-in-jenin/0000018c-6857-de5e-a3ef-6bff5f9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准2023年补充战时预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israel-approves-supplementary-wartime-budget-for-2023/0000018c-6838-de5e-a3ef-6bfd79920000</link><description>该修正案以 58 票赞成、44 票反对的投票结果获得批准。内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团情报部长吉拉·加姆利尔缺席投票，利库德集团议员尤利·埃德尔斯坦最初投了赞成票，但后来要求修改投票以弃权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 12:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israel-approves-supplementary-wartime-budget-for-2023/0000018c-6838-de5e-a3ef-6bfd79920000</guid></item></channel></rss>